The task is to hide rows with `N/A` values in the table but not delete or filter out any cells. Instead, we will programmatically hide rows containing `N/A`. To accomplish this, I will inspect each row and hide it if any cell in the row contains the value `N/A`, leaving the structure of the table intact.
